<header>
<div id="instruction">
	What will you do when you're not sure about something?
</div>
</header>
	
<section id="body">

<div class="brieftext">
<p><b>Look at these expressions:</b></p>

<ol color="#0000FF">
	<li>Sorry, could you repeat that?</li>
	<li>Could you say that again?</li>
	<li>I didn't catch what you said?</li>
	<li>I'm not sure what you mean by ... ?</li>
	<li>Do you mean ... or ... ?</li>
	<li>I'm not sure what "urban" means.</li>
</ol>



<p>Now look at the following clips:</p>

<p>Dimitris realises he has nothing more to say: "Nothing else, really."</p>
</div>

